{
  "id": "RAW_f781df9a",
  "title": "MiniMax M2-her：我们做出了更懂你的 AI",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzE5MTA3NzcxMQ==&mid=2247487576&idx=1&sn=a3a9f1a85d6da00e3e9b40b899d2f50f",
  "date": "2026-01-28 13:43:00",
  "author": "MiniMax 稀宇科技",
  "siteName": "MiniMax 稀宇科技",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fed2b643&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fq4wL2iaHZfGmCqSpwhX0PpzNAQFb3TOmVBRVKWLAOB7uOq00c7jxpJXPQv6F155nIWFz5FfZ5sj1EHGTzY4bI9g%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">今天，我们分享 MiniMax-M2-her 背后的技术思考。M2-her 也是服务星野/Talkie的底层模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">13 年前，电影《Her》描绘了AI系统 Samantha。她温柔、幽默，能同时与 8316 人交谈，却依然让每一个人都感受到自己是被独特理解的那个。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这一维度上，这部电影至今仍定义了我们对 AI 伙伴的终极想象：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">一个模型，实现千人千面，走进每个人的世界。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在星野和 Talkie 的更新迭代中，我们仍在思考：如何让 AI 拥有服务亿万人的能力，依然能让每一个人都觉得，自己与 AI 的对话是独一无二的？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们认为，</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;伙伴的内核，在于</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">用户</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">和这个角色共同</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">编织</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的旅程。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">更深层次的角色扮演，是要让每个用户都能在那个世界里，拥有鲜活的体验，获得只属于自己的那个瞬间。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">它本质刻画的是智能体在特定 [World] × [Stories] 坐标下，针对 [User Preferences] 的演绎能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这三个维度，分别对应 AI 伙伴体验的不同层面：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">World：</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如何让每个世界都长出自己的样子？&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不同人构建的世界千差万别，如果模型只学到平均值，所有角色就会千人一面，所有世界都会坍缩成平庸。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Story：如何让故事</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">再长也有</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">生命力？</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;对话越长，剧情失控风险越高。好的模型能够根据历史状态，选择合适的节奏，避免陷入机械循环；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">User Preferences：如何读懂用户未被言明的期待？</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;用户不会明说，但好模型要能从细节中推断出用户的潜在偏好</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"font-size:36px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 5px 0px 2px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-left: 2px solid rgb(240, 60, 22);padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"width:100%;line-height:1.25;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一步，把新的判卷标准建起来：</span></strong></p>\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Role-Play Bench</span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">传统的用户体验，常用 A/B 测试来获得用户的偏好。但这一做法在模型快速迭代，且用户会对旧版本模型风格产生依赖的当下，存在明显局限。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">陪伴场景的特殊性在于：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不存在可验证的标准答案。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">举例而言，问一个傲娇人设的 AI 角色“你喜欢我吗”，对方回答“哼，才没有”或“你烦不烦啊”都可能是对的。一百个用户有一百种期待，这导致我们无法进行有区分度的评估。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">但是在相同场景下，一个傲娇角色如果回答“是的，我很喜欢你”，就明显人设崩了。因此，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">要</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">定义</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">“</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">什么是用户喜欢的（对齐偏好）</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">”很难</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">但“</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">用户不喜欢什么</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">”</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">能够被清楚定义</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。——这就可以称为 misalignment（非对齐）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">基于这个思路，我们提出了评估标准&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Role-Play Bench，</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">聚焦三个 misalignment 维度：</span></span></strong></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Worlds，</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">模型能否维持复杂世界观：关注是否存在基础文本错误、逻辑混乱、事实性错误等问题，这些问题在长对话中会累积，最终破坏沉浸感；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Stories，</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">模型能否鲜活推进故事：关注表达多样性和叙事逻辑（如角色崩坏）。好的故事应该有呼吸感，而不是套路重复；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">User Preferences，</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">模型能否恰当响应用户：关注是否越界、是否自说自话、是否能避免沉默、是否过度拒绝。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这套评估方法</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">让我们在快速迭代模型的同时</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">对齐真实</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">用户体验</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们对主流模型进行了系统评测，结果显示，在 100 轮的长程对话交互中，MiniMax-M2-her 综合表现位居榜首。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"2450\" data-imgfileid=\"100003918\" data-ratio=\"0.6490066225165563\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"3775\" data-width=\"3775\" style=\"pointer-events: initial;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7b21e19d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fq4wL2iaHZfGmCqSpwhX0PpzNAQFb3TOmVZ0vXRoIINSZGI0OAo7iavmKeoyHsRvHGsQ1MTk3Uic1iaNCtO51rHAZmA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">评测结果显示，M2-her 在 Worlds 维度排名第一。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;模型同时扮演多个角色和旁白时很容易混淆谁在说话，也容易混淆空间逻辑，比如角色和用户已经道别离开了，模型仍让他们隔空对话。</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">M2-her 会用旁白引导时空和事件，让对话自然发展。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"2450\" data-imgfileid=\"100003921\" data-ratio=\"0.6490066225165563\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"3775\" data-width=\"3775\" style=\"pointer-events: initial;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=847a05b0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fq4wL2iaHZfGmCqSpwhX0PpzNAQFb3TOmVZbgXKYauyIp5290d99q43qJWibdt1SgecT7DdAtLHuT8L5KGDzNUkDQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 Stories 维度，M2-her 排名第五，达到较高水准。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">相比 Gemini 的辞藻丰富、Claude 的稳定推进、豆包的表达生动，M2-her 更偏向在平实自然的语言风格下维持多样性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"2450\" data-imgfileid=\"100003919\" data-ratio=\"0.6490066225165563\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"3775\" data-width=\"3775\" style=\"pointer-events: initial;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1ca750a0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fq4wL2iaHZfGmCqSpwhX0PpzNAQFb3TOmVSI5ZccA8zjAx3aF3LoJGM0YFKTwLVv3M7hxGWI6pduz1ibECLYOJ9bA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">User Preference</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">维度，MiniMax-M2-her 表现突出。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">它会避免代替用户发言，同时重视对用户意图的响应、做到自然互动。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"2450\" data-imgfileid=\"100003922\" data-ratio=\"0.6490066225165563\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"3775\" data-width=\"3775\" style=\"pointer-events: initial;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7e006277&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fq4wL2iaHZfGmCqSpwhX0PpzNAQFb3TOmVpGDiam5VbfHoze3yeCfib8sqhsDTsoiczsAT2HVfHw5RADhEQ81BEf4nw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">角色扮演需要长程一致性——持续维持人物、关系与情节的连贯性，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">M2-her 在多轮对话中能更好地维持稳定性。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">大多数模型在 20 轮后便显露疲态。M2-her 进行针对性优化后，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">即便在 100 轮对话中，它依然能将回复长度稳定在最佳区间，在拒绝冗余的同时，确保多样性与高信息密度。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"2379\" data-imgfileid=\"100003920\" data-ratio=\"0.7481481481481481\" data-width=\"3180\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=30a59785&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fq4wL2iaHZfGmCqSpwhX0PpzNAQFb3TOmV0tDkCE1HwTKaA6RKksI3upJEvtsNRhzP7LhWDWwG2DwNGfswR9OGiaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 149, 158);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">各模型随轮次变化的质量与字数趋势图</span></span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"font-size:36px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 5px 0px 2px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-left: 2px solid rgb(240, 60, 22);padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"width:100%;line-height:1.25;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二步，让模型边服务边进化：</span></strong></p>\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Online RLHF</span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Role-Play Bench 解决了评估标准的问题，但如何让模型理解用户的真实偏好？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">用户不会明说“我喜欢慢节奏”，却会在不喜欢的内容里频繁点击“重新生成”，在喜欢的对话里停留更久。</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这些隐式信号，是理解用户真实偏好的关键。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们让模型持续从这些信号中学习，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">核心难点是筛选信号。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;用户的原始行为数据存在噪声，比如：点赞可能出于习惯而非真正喜欢，长时间停留可能只是离开了屏幕。我们对信号本身进行严格筛选，并通过因果推断的方式对信号去噪。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在训练过程中，我们持续监控模型的多样性。当模型开始重复某些固定模式、失去表达多样性时，我们会提前终止训练。训练好的 RL 模型重新部署后，会收集到更高质量的反馈数据，进而训练出更优的下一代模型，形成正向循环。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"1370\" data-imgfileid=\"100003923\" data-ratio=\"0.3074074074074074\" data-width=\"4462\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2836f218&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fq4wL2iaHZfGmCqSpwhX0PpzNAQFb3TOmVe0yibj2ll6jnQr3DJlTia5iaPTtPdicZvWtjZOViaKWOB9P5w8cRZb54gzw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 149, 158);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Online Preference Learning 流程概览</span></span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"font-size:36px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">03</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 5px 0px 2px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-left: 2px solid rgb(240, 60, 22);padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"width:100%;line-height:1.25;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">下一站：共同创造世界</span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">过去，我们专注解决“如何让 AI 扮演好一个角色”的问题。下一步的命题是：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如何让用户真正拥有一个可以探索、改变、生长的世界。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们将这个方向称为</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;Worldplay</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">——让用户从“进入预设世界”升级为“共同创造世界”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这意味着两个关键突破：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">第一，动态的世界记忆。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;你的每个选择都会影响后续剧情，模型需要在数百轮对话中记住“什么发生过、什么因此改变、未来可能发生什么”，就像开放世界游戏里你触发的每个支线都会改变主线走向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">第二，多角色协同叙事。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;当前的关系形式主要是 1v1，但真正精彩的故事往往是群像剧。想象一下：两个角色因你而产生关联，NPC 们在你不在场时也会发生故事。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">最终，我们希望让每个人都能定义自己的世界，让故事在那个世界里自由生长。用户不仅是故事的参与者，更是世界的定义者。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Worlds to Dream, Stories to Live. Let's go together.</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们还有很长的路要走，但方向已经清晰。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">M2-her API 已同步上线MiniMax 开放平台。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">关于评测指标明细与更多细节，可在 Role-play Bench 中查阅。了解完整版技术深度解析，请点击文末“阅读原文”。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">API接入：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">platform.minimaxi.com/docs/api-reference/text-chat</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Role-play Bench:</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">huggingface.co/datasets/MiniMaxAI/role-play-bench</span></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "MiniMax 发布 M2-her 模型，通过 Role-Play Bench 评测体系和 Online RLHF 技术，提升 AI 角色扮演的长程一致性与用户偏好对齐。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "MiniMax 发布 M2-her 模型，通过 Role-Play Bench 评测体系和 Online RLHF 技术，提升 AI 角色扮演的长程一致性与用户偏好对齐。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了 MiniMax 针对角色扮演场景推出的新一代模型 M2-her。文章指出 AI 伙伴的核心在于“世界观、故事感、用户偏好”三个维度的融合。针对角色扮演缺乏客观标准的难题，MiniMax 提出了 Role-Play Bench，通过定义“非对齐（misalignment）”来评估模型在长对话中的表现。技术上，M2-her 采用 Online RLHF 学习用户的隐式反馈（如重新生成、停留时长），并针对长程对话（100 轮以上）的一致性和信息密度进行了深度优化。未来，MiniMax 计划从单向角色扮演转向“Worldplay”，实现动态世界记忆和多角色协同叙事。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "提出以“非对齐”为核心的 Role-Play Bench 评估体系。",
      "explanation": "由于陪伴场景不存在标准答案，MiniMax 通过定义用户不喜欢的“非对齐”维度（如逻辑混乱、角色崩坏、过度拒绝）来建立可量化的判卷标准。"
    },
    {
      "point": "利用 Online RLHF 技术从用户隐式信号中进化模型。",
      "explanation": "模型通过筛选和去噪处理用户在交互中的“重新生成”和“停留时长”等行为数据，形成正向反馈循环，使 AI 更精准地捕捉用户未言明的偏好。"
    },
    {
      "point": "针对长程对话的一致性与多样性进行了深度优化。",
      "explanation": "M2-her 解决了大多数模型在 20 轮对话后出现的疲态，确保在 100 轮交互中仍能维持稳定的回复长度、高信息密度和鲜活的人设。"
    },
    {
      "point": "未来方向将从角色扮演进化为共同创造的“Worldplay”。",
      "explanation": "下一阶段将突破动态世界记忆和多角色协同叙事，让用户的选择能真实改变剧情走向，并实现 NPC 之间的自主关联与故事发生。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "AI 伙伴的内核，在于用户和这个角色共同编织的旅程。",
    "要定义 '什么是用户喜欢的（对齐偏好）' 很难，但 '用户不喜欢什么' 能够被清楚定义。",
    "好的故事应该有呼吸感，而不是套路重复。",
    "这些隐式信号，是理解用户真实偏好的关键。",
    "用户不仅是故事的参与者，更是世界的定义者。"
  ],
